    52("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Source Registries</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>External public OCI<br />registries (Docker Hub, Quay,<br />GHCR) the images originate<br />from.</div>")
    style 52 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    53("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Destination Registries</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>The organization's private<br />OCI registries — any<br />dist-spec registry (Harbor,<br />Zot, …); destination for the<br />stamped images, addressed<br />generically via regctl.</div>")
    style 53 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    54("<div style='font-weight: bold'>BuildKit</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>OCI build engine houba drives<br />to rebuild and harden images.</div>")
    style 54 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    58("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Usage oracle / observability</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Answers 'was this image's<br />content seen in production<br />lately?' (e.g. Datadog).<br />Queried point-in-time by<br />houba purge; never owned by<br />houba.</div>")
    style 58 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    59("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Signing / Key service</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>KMS or Fulcio (keyless CA)<br />that houba's attestor uses to<br />sign in-toto attestations<br />(DSSE). Trust is org<br />configuration, not baked in.</div>")
    style 59 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff
    60("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Transparency log (Rekor)</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Optional append-only<br />signature log; blank in<br />air-gapped orgs. houba can<br />point at one but never<br />deploys it.</div>")
    style 60 fill:#0f766e,stroke:#0a524d,color:#ffffff
    61("<div style='font-weight: bold'>Vulnerability scanner</div><div style='font-size: 70%; margin-top: 0px'>[Software System]</div><div style='font-size: 80%; margin-top:10px'>Emits SARIF vulnerability<br />reports. houba relates to it<br />two ways: it INGESTS a report<br />produced in CI / a scan<br />service (attach), and INVOKES<br />a configured one on the SBOM<br />at admission (scanstep gate,<br />HOUBA_SCAN_EVALUATOR_CMD).<br />houba owns neither the tool<br />nor its CVE database.</div>")
    style 61 fill:#69707a,stroke:#494e55,color:#ffffff

